OL,3,CPolice searching River Irwell for
OL,4,Cmissing boy
OL,6,FSpecialist search teams are looking
OL,7,Ffor a boy who got into difficulty in a
OL,8,Friver in Salford.
OL,10,FGreater Manchester Police said the boy
OL,11,Fwas last seen just before 5pm on
OL,12,FSaturday in the River Irwell at
OL,13,FClifton Country Park in Salford.
OL,15,FA force spokesperson said: "Emergency
OL,16,Fservices and specialist search teams
OL,17,Fremain at the scene. The incident is
OL,18,Fongoing."
OL,20,FNo further details about the boy have
OL,21,Fbeen released.
